---
title: Context & Research Sequence
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant CLI as CLI Command
    participant Orch as Orchestration Core
    participant CtxAgg as Context Aggregator
    participant ResCo as Research Coordinator
    participant PRDEng as PRD Engine
    participant SpecComp as Specification Composer
    participant RunStore as Run Storage
    participant Agent as Agent Adapter

    Note over CLI,Agent: Phase 1: Context Gathering & Discovery

    CLI->>Orch: start feature (prompt/Linear/spec)
    activate Orch

    Orch->>CtxAgg: aggregateContext(featureId, config)
    activate CtxAgg

    Note over CtxAgg: Discover files via globs<br/>Hash files (incremental)<br/>Rank by score + token budget

    CtxAgg->>RunStore: Store file_hashes.json
    CtxAgg->>RunStore: Store context/summary.json
    CtxAgg-->>Orch: ContextDocument + diagnostics
    deactivate CtxAgg

    Note over CLI,Agent: Phase 2: Research Task Detection

    Orch->>ResCo: detectUnknownsFromContext(contextDoc)
    activate ResCo
    Orch-->>ResCo: prompt/spec text + manualUnknowns
    ResCo->>ResCo: scanPromptAndSpec(TBD/TODO/??? markers)
    ResCo->>ResCo: scanContextFiles(max 12, README/docs)

    Note over ResCo: Analyze context + prompt/spec<br/>Identify TBD/TODO markers<br/>Generate objectives + sources

    loop For each unknown
        ResCo->>ResCo: generateCacheKey(objectives, sources)

        alt Cached task exists and fresh
            ResCo->>RunStore: Load cached task
            RunStore-->>ResCo: Cached ResearchTask
            Note over ResCo: Mark as 'cached'<br/>Reuse existing results
        else Create new task
            ResCo->>ResCo: createResearchTask(taskId, objectives)
            ResCo->>RunStore: Save research/tasks/{taskId}.json<br/>Include detection metadata + freshness
            ResCo->>RunStore: Append research/tasks.jsonl
            Note over ResCo: Status: 'pending'
        end
    end

    ResCo-->>Orch: List of ResearchTask[]
    deactivate ResCo

    Note over CLI,Agent: Phase 3: Research Execution (Optional)

    opt Execute research tasks
        loop For each pending task
            Orch->>ResCo: startTask(taskId)
            activate ResCo
            ResCo->>RunStore: Update task status='in_progress'
            ResCo-->>Orch: Updated task
            deactivate ResCo

            Orch->>Agent: Query sources (codebase/web/API)
            activate Agent
            Agent-->>Orch: Research findings
            deactivate Agent

            Orch->>ResCo: completeTask(taskId, results)
            activate ResCo
            ResCo->>RunStore: Update task with results<br/>Store confidence score<br/>Record sources consulted
            ResCo-->>Orch: Completed task
            deactivate ResCo
        end
    end

    Note over CLI,Agent: Phase 4: PRD/Spec Authoring with Context

    Orch->>PRDEng: generatePRD(contextDoc, researchTasks)
    activate PRDEng

    Note over PRDEng: Assemble prompt with:<br/>- Context summaries<br/>- Research results<br/>- User requirements

    PRDEng->>Agent: Generate PRD draft
    activate Agent
    Agent-->>PRDEng: PRD content
    deactivate Agent

    PRDEng->>RunStore: Save artifacts/prd.md
    PRDEng-->>Orch: PRD document
    deactivate PRDEng

    Orch->>SpecComp: generateSpec(prd, contextDoc, researchTasks)
    activate SpecComp

    Note over SpecComp: Assemble prompt with:<br/>- PRD requirements<br/>- Context references<br/>- Research outputs

    SpecComp->>Agent: Generate specification
    activate Agent
    Agent-->>SpecComp: Spec content
    deactivate Agent

    SpecComp->>RunStore: Save artifacts/spec.md
    SpecComp-->>Orch: Specification document
    deactivate SpecComp

    Orch-->>CLI: Feature initialized with context + research
    deactivate Orch

    Note over CLI,Agent: CLI Commands for Research Management

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note right of CLI: ai-feature research list<br/>Shows all research tasks<br/>with status and cache info

        CLI->>ResCo: listTasks(filters)
        activate ResCo
        ResCo->>RunStore: Load research/tasks/*.json
        RunStore-->>ResCo: Task files
        ResCo-->>CLI: Filtered ResearchTask[]
        deactivate ResCo
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note right of CLI: ai-feature research show {taskId}<br/>Displays task details<br/>and results

        CLI->>ResCo: getTask(taskId)
        activate ResCo
        ResCo->>RunStore: Load research/tasks/{taskId}.json
        RunStore-->>ResCo: ResearchTask
        ResCo-->>CLI: Task with results
        deactivate ResCo
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note right of CLI: Automatic rate limit handling<br/>and offline fallbacks

        alt Rate limit hit
            Agent-->>Orch: RateLimitError
            Note over Orch: Record in rate_limits.json<br/>Queue tasks for retry
        else Service offline (Linear/GitHub)
            Agent-->>Orch: ServiceUnavailableError
            Note over Orch: Mark tasks as 'pending'<br/>Log warning + fallback
        end
    end
